% Suggest human-approved patches for prompt source-set findings.

You may only propose edits to the primary `.prompt` file or `user_stories/story__*.md` files.
Do NOT modify generated code under `src/`, `pdd/`, or `tests/`.

<prompt_path>{prompt_path}</prompt_path>

<findings>
{findings_json}
</findings>

<prompt_content>
{prompt_content}
</prompt_content>

Return JSON only. Each patch must include the full new file content:

```json
{
  "patches": [
    {
      "path": "relative/path/to/file.prompt",
      "reason": "why this change helps",
      "new_content": "full file text after the edit"
    }
  ]
}
```

If no safe patch is warranted, return `"patches": []`.
